<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink124">
<l>kaṇṭiku mallamō koṇkaniṉ kēḷē</l>
<l>teṇṭirai pāvai vauva</l>
<l>vuṇkaṇ civappa vaḻutuniṉ ṟōḷē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We have seen your friend, haven't we, oh man from the maritime tract?</l>
<l>She who stood crying, so that her kajal-lined eyes reddened,</l>
<l>As the clear waves snatched her doll?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
